{"id": 1919, "genre": 1001, "title": "对于你之前和现在所处的感情关系，你有过哪些困惑？", "description": "现代人离能被明确解释的关系越来越远，越来越多的感情进入“稳定的不确定”状态，你也有类似的感受吗？", "record_count": 2843, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/201709201018311YflCZkya3LPbvRo.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-09-23T17:00:30Z", "options": [{"id": 237568, "content": "不知道因为什么，他冷下来了\n可能是我说错什么了\n但其实相处已经有问题了\n是我自欺欺人\n本来想当面谈一谈，好好告个别\n后来他都不肯主动联系我\n只好“急匆匆开始，急匆匆结束”\n像是一场独角戏\n估计以后我可能会觉得，压根没跟他在一起过\n可能是做梦也不一定哦?", "image": null, "praise_count": 46, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1132645}, {"id": 237569, "content": "不知道對方在想什麽，不想揣測", "image": null, "praise_count": 30, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1136516}, {"id": 237825, "content": "也时常感觉自己单身\n偶尔想想原来认识贺先生九年\n原来我老公姓贺\n\n哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1140323}, {"id": 237570, "content": "汪", "image": null, "praise_count": 97, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 899562}, {"id": 237826, "content": "三年了我们都成熟了也变成了更好的彼此，为什么就不能重新开始呢？我为我之前的任性道歉好吗？", "image": "img/option/option/20170925091426H1R8cE7dDWLUweXG", "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 617465}, {"id": 238594, "content": "表白简单，等待很难.", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1128744}, {"id": 237571, "content": "好像是我在孤军奋战", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1137714}, {"id": 238595, "content": "你的一次离别，把我丢进了突入其来的寂寞当中，让我再难习惯独自相处，最难的是偶尔会想起你.", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1128744}, {"id": 237572, "content": "经常都不确定是不是遵从内心了，都让时间给我答案，包括工作中接触到的一下好的不得了的同事误以为是朋友，一下进去热恋的男友，时间都慢慢给了我想要的答案", "image": null, "praise_count": 18, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1127350}, {"id": 237573, "content": "我是不是要孤独终老", "image": null, "praise_count": 77, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 660957}, {"id": 238853, "content": "我喜欢的人不喜欢我", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1057046}, {"id": 237574, "content": "长居伦敦的女朋友当时很快表了白，我说了好。虽然那时离我回国只有三周。而且她知道我原本是个直女。", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 772677}, {"id": 237830, "content": "奔50，依然惑……", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1140336}, {"id": 237575, "content": "我是不是要孤独终老", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 660957}, {"id": 237831, "content": "一个人的时候会想有人陪多好，有人陪的时候又觉得一个人独处更好", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 702056}, {"id": 237832, "content": "现在的交往都很淡，哪天你退一步，我就会退三步，然后过两天又重新走回来，或者就再也不联系了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 905362}, {"id": 237577, "content": "确定喜欢她 但内心还是有点距离感 像错过什么一样 她的人生 她的经历 她的一切！", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1139397}, {"id": 238857, "content": "两人不在一个世界，不在一个平台。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1143661}, {"id": 237578, "content": "说完我喜欢你，我就不喜欢你了", "image": null, "praise_count": 177, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 928618}, {"id": 237579, "content": "之前感觉找个儿子！现在自己变成小公主", "image": null, "praise_count": 15, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1139402}, {"id": 237835, "content": "自以为遇见了Dream One，1年暧昧，人家不过是想睡睡玩玩。他说他想恋爱了，毫不犹豫的离开了", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1140385}, {"id": 237580, "content": "很焦虑，不安，翻他聊天记录，", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 769744}, {"id": 237836, "content": "间歇性疑惑我们到底是好基友还是好情侣？微信聊天永远都是在就事论事讨论各种社会问题和爱好，完全没有打情骂俏，所以热度也一直升不起来？虽然我觉得挺舒服的。但是外人觉得我可能谈了个假恋爱。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 113539}, {"id": 237581, "content": "患得患失 总觉得自己不够好 没办法带给别人快乐 然后独自在自己的世界里沉沦 拒绝出去 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 51, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 903543}, {"id": 237838, "content": "骗还是骗不了自己", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 930622}, {"id": 240911, "content": "一个人挺好", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1151223}, {"id": 237840, "content": "老鹿不撞", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 961662}, {"id": 237585, "content": "有一天我也会变得讳莫如深，我知道", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1035373}, {"id": 237841, "content": "与其与你苟活，不如孤独终老", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1140408}, {"id": 237843, "content": "不知怎么就联系变淡了，找不到理由，但我知道是我的错。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1140412}, {"id": 237588, "content": "没有另一半，这是我最大的疑问", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1073481}, {"id": 237589, "content": "和前女友之前都没有恋爱过，恋爱过程充满了尴尬", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 915794}, {"id": 237590, "content": "是的，不想因为太老而坑了她人", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 699564}, {"id": 237846, "content": "看不见摸不着\n空有一个头衔", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1192542}, {"id": 237591, "content": "表面说着喜欢结果却跟另外的人在一起吧…", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1118154}, {"id": 238359, "content": "明明知道得慢慢来但是总是操之过急 忍也忍不住", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 814636}, {"id": 237592, "content": "因为最好的女性朋友智障，自己感觉很无助?", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 805579}, {"id": 237593, "content": "有时候觉得他有点喜欢你，有时候又觉得他不过是无聊找个人陪。", "image": null, "praise_count": 68, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1139411}, {"id": 237849, "content": "好久不见，约了我2次才成功见了面。以前见我都挺随便，感觉这次好像稍微收拾了一下，然而见了面表现得很冷淡。问他：“怎么不理我？”他说：“不想理就不理咯，搞笑。”于是我跑了，又打了2个电话让我回去找他，第一次对他发飙吼。到底是想怎样？简直精神分裂...", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 915717}, {"id": 237594, "content": "管撩不管聊，不想负责", "image": null, "praise_count": 16, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 235507}, {"id": 237595, "content": "不见面的时候觉得很想念  见面了却无话可说", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1125125}, {"id": 237596, "content": "很难喜欢上一个人，追求完美", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1139453}, {"id": 246812, "content": "我爱的是你爱我", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 89700}, {"id": 237597, "content": "随着年纪的增大，对高中时代的闺蜜的称呼逐渐变成了高中时代的好朋友、高中的朋友、高中同学。越来越喜欢一个人呆着，不想认识新朋友也懒得与旧友联络感情。", "image": null, "praise_count": 17, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 833260}, {"id": 237598, "content": "我就觉得越长大越孤单，发现自己好像失去了许多朋友，责备自己不优秀", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1139066}, {"id": 240158, "content": "不过是寂寞了想找个人陪", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 886307}, {"id": 237599, "content": "告白是最后的冲锋号\n所以还没告诉她\n但没有确定关系地对她好\n比较尬", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 800043}, {"id": 237600, "content": "婚姻恐惧症怎么解？", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1279464}, {"id": 237602, "content": "这话题让单身狗怎么想", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1139120}, {"id": 238370, "content": "磨合地非常好，好到连嘴都不吵", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1141796}]}